Jul 6, 2024 - Christine Marie Evert Born: December 21, 1954 Fort Lauderdale, FL 
Won at least one Grand Slam event per year for 13 consecutive years 1974-1986
Tournament title victories: 157
Match record: 1309-146
Evert won three Wimbledon single titles (1974, 1976, 1981). 
Evert won a record six US Open singles titles (1975, 1976, 1977, 1978, 1980, 1982)
Evert won a record seven French Open singles titles (1974, 1975, 1979, 1980, 1983, 1985, 1986)
Evert won two Australian Open single titles (1982, 1984). See more ideas about chris evert, wimbledon, chris.
